components.label: Name of person who will be our point of contact:
Content
components.html:
1. Certificate of Incorporation.
  2. Articles of Association and other governing documents.
  3. Latest register of directors and shareholders, or registry extract, or Certificate of Incumbency dated within the last six months.
  4. Certificate of Good Standing, if available in your jurisdiction, dated within the last six months.
  5. Board resolution appointing authorised signatories and specimen signature card.
  6. For ultimate beneficial owners (individuals that ultimately own or control 10% or more of the shares or the voting rights in the body corporate), directors, and for those authorised signatories that will sign contractual documents to bind the company: (a) identity page of valid passport; (b) address proof (front and back of government ID or bank statement, utility bill or government tax letter posted to home address – no mobile phone bills, e-statements or P.O. box mailing addresses); (c) If country of residence different to nationality, please provide proof of right to reside (i.e. long-term visa; employment pass; permanent residence ID).
  7. If there are intermediary layers/ multiple layers of ownership, please provide an ownership and control structure diagram, containing a signed attestation as to its accuracy by a director(s) authorised to bind the company, that illustrates the following for each intermediary layer: (a) full legal name; (b)country of incorporation; (c) incorporation/ registered number; (d) percentage of ownership; (e) type (i.e. corporate; trust, partnership).
  8. Information on source of wealth for each ultimate beneficial owner and source of funds.
  9. Front and last page of all documents are to be signed by a director(s) authorised to bind the company with an attestation next to each signature{s} that certifies authenticity.
  10. Board resolution authorising custody of shares by ProximaX CSD.
